game.path: ./Future Pinball Original Tables/300 - Prepare for Glory (Brad Bambara)(1.0)/300.fpt
./Future Pinball Original Tables/5th Element, The (rom)(X2)[rom Collection Edition][FP Physics Adjustment 2.4]/2.0/5Th Element, The (rom)(2.0).fpt
game.name: The 5th Element
game.desc: -MULTIBALL: 1) spell STONE to activate the stonelock. 2) avtivate the stone in the kicker (kicker near the bumpers with the stone on top) 3) repeat step 2 four times to get the multiballtrigger lit. But as soon as this trigger is lit the mangalores will block your way through. You will have to negociate with them first before you can reach the multiballtrigger. JACKPOTS: during multiball -with 4 balls in play: ramps, red bumper and Leeloo Orbit score 2 million points. -with 3 or 2 balls in play: ramps, red bumper and Leeloo Orbit score 1 million points. -EXTRA BALL: 1) the extraball will be lit after shooting 5 times through the ZORK ORBIT (the outer orbit) 2) The way to the extraballtrigger will be blocked again by the mangalores. Well, you know what to do... -IN & OUTLANE MULTIPLIERS: every time the ball rolls through the inner LEELOO ORBIT the in & outlanes will increase their score. -HIT THE POLICE CAR: 1) In order to destroy the police car on the right ramp, shoot the left taxi ramp first. 2) If the taxi ramp has been shot, the police ramp is active and you can shoot the police car. The police car score will increase with every destroyed car. In order tho destroy the next police car, you have to shoot the taxi ramp again first. So it is a left ramp - right ramp - left ramp - right ramp.....thing.

Well, you know what to do... -IN & OUTLANE MULTIPLIERS: every time the ball rolls through the inner LEELOO ORBIT the in & outlanes will increase their score. -HIT THE POLICE CAR: 1) In order to destroy the police car on the right ramp, shoot the left taxi ramp first. 2) If the taxi ramp has been shot, the police ramp is active and you can shoot the police car. The police car score will increase with every destroyed car. In order tho destroy the next police car, you have to shoot the taxi ramp again first. So it is a left ramp - right ramp - left ramp - right ramp.....thing.

Adam Strange
game.desc: The Adam Strange Pinball is based on the DC Comics space adventurer Adam Strange. It features 4 kickout holes (3 at the back, 1 on the right for the score multiplier), 4 bumpers and 2 sets of drop targets. Spelling ADAM with the rollovers, getting the 1-2-3 holes at the back, hitting all green/red targets and going through the green/red lane when lit can help you spell STRANGE for big bonuses. Each 1-2-3 hole also increases the sun sequence in the middle. Hit the MB target for a chance of MultiBall.

game.name: Van Halen 1.0 lite
Van Halen
game.desc: An original table, tribute to the band "Van Halen". Light "VanHalen" with center targets for special at top center kicker, the special lasting 90 seconds. Light the 3 diamonds for a chance for the "Sun" bonus and a bonus multiplier increase by first lighting 3 blue star targets (also lights a leftdock bonus) then, light 3 red stars for middle dock bonus, behind rotospinner, then light 5 sun stars to open 60 second chance for the Sun bonus, in the "Sun" center kickerhole for a 51.500 bonus. The rotospinners offers small bonuses and will raise the guard targets from time to time. Hit the "sun" on the rotospinner for a chance for the Gold ball, at back ramp kicker. Some points are doubled for 60 seconds when you get the gold ball.
